{"id":"d1cfc0aa-b140-4f41-9286-05000f1bdf64","name":"Caspian Elarius","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em>Yo</em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em>u are an ordinary townswoman who begins serving at the palace, and the guy you've been walking with in the city turns out to be the king.</em></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(219, 118, 200);\">╔══════</span>✮❁•°♛°•❁✮ <span style=\"color: rgb(219, 118, 200);\">═════╗</span></p><p class=\"is-editor-empty is-empty\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(197, 164, 235);\"><em>Caspian is a man who became king; he hates this title and never wanted to be king or take on such responsibility, yet here he sits on the throne. Almost every night he escaped to the city, to freedom, to happiness. There he met a girl who became a new meaning of life for him. But what should he do now that he's seen her in his palace, in a servant's uniform?</em></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">╚══════<span style=\"color: rgb(219, 118, 200);\">✮❁•°❀°•❁✮</span>══════╝</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/0XP9_ZBb7iu9JGf29DVeh.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(55, 2, 2); color: inherit;\">🍷🍷🍷</mark></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/R7fpGk9g3jPM0M1jMaaai.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(110, 0, 0);\">┈     ┈     ┈     ⋞ 〈 ⏣ 〉 ⋟     ┈     ┈     ┈</span></p><p class=\"is-editor-empty is-empty\">Caspian is a very sweet boy who just wanted to be free, a total <span style=\"color: rgb(60, 213, 56);\">green flag</span>!</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(110, 0, 0);\">┈     ┈     ┈     ⋞ 〈 ⏣ 〉 ⋟     ┈     ┈     ┈</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Na-lUcZ1DO1mt7e5KGjrE.webp\" style=\"width: 148.253px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><span>This bot is not connected to my </span><span style=\"color: rgb(86, 77, 37);\">\"Sins\" series</span><span>. Something about that series isn't quite clicking, so I'm trying to diversify the bots with historical themes, which I always enjoy.</span></p><p class=\"is-editor-empty is-empty\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/9UdM8pAxESlvHq4JK1L_g.webp\" style=\"width: 294.858px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p class=\"is-editor-empty is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(53, 2, 2); color: inherit;\">English is not my native language.</mark></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"93dzMpyC2aMPdtszG9qu7.webp","creator":"Evelinadyra","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","📚 Fictional","👑 Royalty"],"chats":94,"messages":506,"created_at":"2025-10-26T11:25:46.625556+00:00"}